# Energy

Gives a real time current month's usage of Gas and Electricity Services. Also gives an estimate of the next billing cycle's usage.



## Usage [/usage/current/month/{accountNumber}]

### Current Month [GET]
Returns current month's usage information for the provided customer id.

+ Parameters
    + accountNumber: 4859634 (number) - Customer's account number.
    
+ Request

    + Headers
    
            tenant-id: 1 (number) - Customer's tenant-id
            api-key: f3ae03ca-0937-4510-be76-775d6ada45e2 (number) 

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        
        {
            "account_number": "4859634",
            "name": "Darko",
            "email": "b@b.com",
            "gas_usage": "20,006 Btu",
